title: "Trusting the trustless blockchain for its adoption in accounting: theorizing the mediating role of technology-organization-environment framework"
year: 2025
main_author: Sujata Seshadrinathan and Shalini Chandra
main_contribution: This study establishes a trust-centric model using the Technology-Organization-Environment (TOE) framework to explain how trust in blockchain technology facilitates its adoption in the accounting industry by mediating technological, organizational, and environmental factors.
evidence_type: Journal Article (Financial Innovation)
